in females; general color pale yellowish orange with darker brown hemelytra. SURFACE AND VESTITURE. 
<emphasis id="B92BEACEFFE37F09FA93DC8BFA1AF4EF" box="[1368,1429,478,504]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="207">
<location id="8E806007FFE37F09FA93DC8BFA1AF4EF" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F687CAFFE07F09FF5CDB8DFE72F3F2:8E806007FFE37F09FA93DC8BFA1AF4EF" box="[1368,1429,478,504]" county="Relatively" municipality="Legs" name="Head" pageId="6" pageNumber="207">Head</location>
</emphasis>
: 
<location id="8E806007FFE37F09FF5CDF57FF7EF70B" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F687CAFFE07F09FF5CDB8DFE72F3F2:8E806007FFE37F09FF5CDF57FF7EF70B" box="[151,241,514,540]" county="Relatively" municipality="Legs" name="Smooth" pageId="6" pageNumber="207">Smooth</location>
